data.description: Situated on a flat oversized lot and within minutes to Offutt AFB, interstate access, & shopping/dining, this gorgeous Cedar Grove ranch will blow you away from the front door.  Classic engineered hardwoods greet you as you step into the entry way along with the open concept living, dining, and kitchen space.  This beauty boasts newer carpet in living/bedroom spaces and a beautifully updated kitchen which includes an elegant subway tile backsplash, refreshed cabinetry, & quartz countertops.  From there, stroll back to the 3 large main level bedrooms including an opulent primary suite boasting versatile design touches and a tiled en suite bathroom with dual sinks, oodles of storage, & a luxurious tiled walk-in shower.  Don't forget to check out the fully finished basement w/everything needed for football game days including a wet bar and a fully wired surround sound system (plus the 4th conforming bedroom and a 5th non conforming "flex space"). This one won't last!
